I gotta call you back.

995
00:51:38.846 --> 00:51:39.680
Kill who?

996
00:51:39.806 --> 00:51:40.973
Krystal.

997
00:51:41.516 --> 00:51:42.636
Don't even try bullshittin'.

998
00:51:42.767 --> 00:51:43.893
Police said it was you.

999
00:51:44.060 --> 00:51:45.061
Somebody saw you.

1000
00:51:45.228 --> 00:51:46.521
Police got it wrong.

1001
00:51:47.313 --> 00:51:48.397
Just like always.

1002
00:51:48.564 --> 00:51:51.108
Everybody always got
it wrong. but you.

1003
00:51:52.068 --> 00:51:53.068
As far as you concerned.

1004
00:51:53.194 --> 00:51:54.546
you ain't never done
nothin' to nobody.

1005
00:51:54.570 --> 00:51:55.822
Nah.

1006
00:51:58.574 --> 00:51:59.867
<i>I've done shit. Kanan.</i>

1007
00:52:02.370 --> 00:52:04.163
Shit I wish I'd never done.

1008
00:52:06.249 --> 00:52:07.416
To you.

1009
00:52:08.459 --> 00:52:10.521
To other people in my life
that I love and I care about.

1010
00:52:10.545 --> 00:52:12.463
But I didn't kill
your girlfriend.

1011
00:52:13.714 --> 00:52:15.901
And I swear to that on the most
important thing in my life.

1012
00:52:15.925 --> 00:52:17.301
and that's my child.

1013
00:52:18.928 --> 00:52:19.929
You.

1014
00:52:21.055 --> 00:52:23.975
I swear on you. Kanan. that I
didn't do nothin' to Krystal.

1015
00:52:24.433 --> 00:52:26.602
You don't give a fuck about me.

1016
00:52:26.727 --> 00:52:27.727
You my life.

1017
00:52:29.730 --> 00:52:31.065
You always been my life.

1018
00:52:31.649 --> 00:52:33.568
You ain't allowed
to say all that

1019
00:52:33.734 --> 00:52:35.403
when you do what
you've done to me.

1020
00:52:36.404 --> 00:52:38.590
Know what the most fucked up
part of this shit is. though?

1021
00:52:38.614 --> 00:52:40.408
I know you killed Fame too.

1022
00:52:40.575 --> 00:52:41.993
- I didn't.
- You did.

1023
00:52:42.159 --> 00:52:43.536
I know you did.

1024
00:52:44.328 --> 00:52:45.454
What's so fucked up is that

1025
00:52:45.621 --> 00:52:47.623
that wasn't enough for
me to do this right here.

1026
00:52:48.624 --> 00:52:50.960
You twisted up my
brain so bad...

1027
00:52:51.127 --> 00:52:53.421
you killin' my best
friend wasn't enough.

1028
00:52:54.589 --> 00:52:55.923
I made excuses for you.

1029
00:52:56.340 --> 00:52:57.884
<i>Maybe Fame was snitchin'.</i>

1030
00:52:58.843 --> 00:53:00.737
<i>Maybe you knew somethin'
about him I didn't know.</i>

1031
00:53:00.761 --> 00:53:03.014
I came up with reasons for you

1032
00:53:03.180 --> 00:53:06.100
to explain why you killed
my best fuckin' friend.

1033
00:53:07.768 --> 00:53:09.020
I'm always protecting you.

1034
00:53:09.186 --> 00:53:11.147
[tense music playing]

1035
00:53:11.314 --> 00:53:12.481
But not no more.

1036
00:53:13.190 --> 00:53:15.735
I'm done makin' excuses
for you and for me.

1037
00:53:15.902 --> 00:53:17.904
Tonight. I'ma do
what I shoulda done.

1038
00:53:20.948 --> 00:53:22.491
I would never hurt
you like that.

1039
00:53:23.409 --> 00:53:25.578
You don't believe me
because you in so much pain.

1040
00:53:26.370 --> 00:53:27.370
But I love you.

1041
00:53:27.496 --> 00:53:30.124
Only person you
ever loved is you!

1042
00:53:30.291 --> 00:53:32.001
<i>You don't know how
to love nobody else.</i>

1043
00:53:32.168 --> 00:53:35.546
Why would I kill Krystal.
Kanan? Why would I do that?

1044
00:53:35.713 --> 00:53:38.716
Because you don't want me
to have nobody but you.

1045
00:53:39.258 --> 00:53:40.801
<i>Want me all to
your-fuckin'-self.</i>

1046
00:53:40.968 --> 00:53:42.470
That's why you killed 'em all.

1047
00:53:42.595 --> 00:53:44.889
D. Fame. Krystal.

1048
00:53:45.306 --> 00:53:47.224
Even my own fuckin' father!

1049
00:53:49.852 --> 00:53:52.021
That's why I gotta
do this right now.

1050
00:53:54.774 --> 00:53:57.610
So you can't take nobody
else away from me.

1051
00:53:57.777 --> 00:54:01.739
[tense. ominous music playing]

1052
00:54:22.093 --> 00:54:24.345
[music intensifies]

1053
00:54:25.513 --> 00:54:26.347
[music fades]

1054
00:54:26.514 --> 00:54:27.556
[gunshot echoes]

1055
00:54:27.723 --> 00:54:30.434
[older Kanan] <i>Fuck
you gonna say? What?</i>

1056
00:54:30.601 --> 00:54:33.896
<i>♪ Please allow me To
introduce myself ♪</i>

1057
00:54:34.021 --> 00:54:38.234
<i>♪ I'm a man of
wealth And taste ♪</i>

1058
00:54:39.151 --> 00:54:42.405
<i>♪ I've been around For
a long. long year ♪</i>

1059
00:54:42.571 --> 00:54:46.117
<i>♪ Stole many a man's
Soul and faith ♪</i>

1060
00:54:47.201 --> 00:54:50.538
<i>♪ And I was 'round
When Jesus Christ ♪</i>

1061
00:54:50.663 --> 00:54:54.667
<i>♪ Had his moment
Of doubt and pain ♪</i>

1062
00:54:55.668 --> 00:54:58.546
<i>♪ Made damn sure that Pilate ♪</i>

1063
00:54:58.713 --> 00:55:02.675
<i>♪ Washed his hands
And sealed his fate ♪</i>

1064
00:55:03.592 --> 00:55:04.592
<i>♪ Ooh ♪</i>

1065
00:55:06.178 --> 00:55:10.891
<i>♪ Pleased to meet you
Hope you guess my name ♪</i>

1066
00:55:12.768 --> 00:55:18.274
<i>♪ But what's puzzling you
Is the nature of my game ♪</i>

1067
00:55:18.441 --> 00:55:21.944
["Sympathy for the Devil" by
The Rolling Stones playing]

1068
00:55:22.111 --> 00:55:25.406
<i>♪ I stuck around
St. Petersburg ♪</i>

1069
00:55:25.573 --> 00:55:29.160
<i>♪ When I saw it was
a time For a change ♪</i>

1070
00:55:30.870 --> 00:55:33.581
<i>♪ Killed the Czar
And his ministers ♪</i>

1071
00:55:33.748 --> 00:55:37.501
<i>♪ Anastasia screamed in vain ♪</i>

1072
00:55:38.711 --> 00:55:39.879
<i>♪ I rode a tank... ♪</i>
